data.description: Beautifully renovated 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on 1.58 acres in Pickens, SC awaits your future. All new neutral paint and flooring throughout gives you a blank canvas upon which to add your favorite colors. With a recent roof, brand new HVAC and new stainless appliances, this home should be low maintenance for years to come. Modern touches and new lighting accent every room. Updated kitchen and baths make you proud to host family and friends. New french doors and deck off the dining room allow your gatherings to easily spill into your backyard AND approximately 1 acre of wooded land beyond the cleared area. All this, and only minutes to our area's most beautiful lakes, mountains, and waterfalls. Convenient to downtown Pickens' bustling Main Street and the northern end of the Doodle Trail. Come see this countryside paradise today - you're gonna love it!
